N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.9 - Entries to be posted

State Regulations

Entries to all races, excepting those which are opened
and decided during the meeting, shall be posted on the bulletin commissions at
the track where meeting is being held. Notes
